BeyondSingleObject / Multi-3DLLM

This repository contains code for the CVPR 2026 Findings paper:
"BeyondSingleObject: Learning 3D Relations with Large Language Models".

Portions of this codebase and the public data recipe are derived from or use
PointLLM and related open-source projects. See the README acknowledgements for
upstream project links, licenses, and dataset terms.
